name: Community Art Frame
description:
Create your own art and add it to the Figma Community art gallery!

---

Duplicate this file and create a piece of art that fits in the 800px square frame. You can base your art off of one of the included prompts, or on whatever you like! When you're done, put your art in the included frame and fill out the information on the attribution card, then publish it as a remix to this file so we can see all the art in one place!
